Beginner Level Projects
To-Do List: Create a simple to-do list where users can add, delete, and mark tasks as completed.
Calculator: Build a basic calculator that performs addition, subtraction, multiplication, and division.
Countdown Timer: Develop a countdown timer that allows users to set a specific time and counts down to zero.
Random Quote Generator: Create a page that displays a random quote from an array of quotes each time a button is clicked.
Color Picker: Build a tool where users can pick a color from a color palette and see the corresponding hex code.
Image Slider: Implement a simple image slider that cycles through a set of images.
Weather App: Use a weather API to display the current weather of a user’s location.
Currency Converter: Build a currency converter that fetches exchange rates and converts amounts between currencies.
Form Validation: Create a form with various input fields and implement validation for each field.
Number Guessing Game: Develop a game where the user has to guess a number between a certain range and receives feedback on their guess.
Intermediate Level Projects
Memory Game: Create a memory card game where users have to match pairs of cards.
Movie Search App: Use a movie API to build an app where users can search for movies and view details.
Todo List with Local Storage: Enhance the basic to-do list to save tasks in the browser’s local storage.
Recipe App: Create an app that allows users to search for recipes and view ingredients and instructions.
Expense Tracker: Build an app that tracks income and expenses and displays a summary.
Chat Application: Develop a simple chat application using WebSockets or a third-party service like Firebase.
Markdown Previewer: Create a live preview tool for markdown text.
Pomodoro Timer: Implement a Pomodoro timer that helps users manage their time with work and break intervals.
Personal Portfolio: Build a personal portfolio website to showcase your projects and skills.
Interactive Quiz: Develop a quiz app that presents multiple-choice questions and shows the score at the end.
Advanced Level Projects
E-commerce Website: Build a small e-commerce website with features like product listings, a shopping cart, and a checkout process.
Blog Platform: Create a blog platform where users can create, edit, and delete posts, and leave comments.
Task Management App: Develop a more complex to-do list with features like categories, priorities, and deadlines.
Real-time Collaborative Editor: Build a text editor that allows multiple users to edit the same document in real-time.
Social Media Dashboard: Create a dashboard that displays various metrics from social media platforms using their APIs.
Online Code Editor: Implement an online code editor with syntax highlighting and real-time output.
Weather Dashboard: Build a dashboard that shows the weather for multiple locations with detailed forecasts.
Music Player: Create a web-based music player with playlist management and playback controls.
Fitness Tracker: Develop an app that tracks workouts, sets goals, and provides statistics on progress.
Virtual Keyboard: Implement an on-screen virtual keyboard that users can interact with.